\int_{0}^{L} \omega_i^2 Y_i(x)Y_j(x) dx &amp;= \int_{0}^{L} \frac{{{\partial ^2}Y_i\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}Y_j(x) dx \\
&amp;=\left . \frac{{{\partial}Y_i\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} \frac{{{\partial}Y_j\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} \right|_{0}^{L} - \int_0^L \frac{{{\partial}Y_i\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} \frac{{{\partial}Y_j\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} dx \\
&amp;= (\frac{k}{T})^2Y_i(x)Y_j(x) - \int_0^L \frac{{{\partial}Y_i\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} \frac{{{\partial}Y_j\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} dx
\end{align*}
$$

同理有

$$\int_{0}^{L} \omega_j^2 Y_i(x)Y_j(x) dx = (\frac{k}{T})^2Y_i(x)Y_j(x) - \int_0^L \frac{{{\partial}Y_i\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} \frac{{{\partial}Y_j\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} dx$$

所以

$$(\omega_i^2 - \omega_j^2)\int_0^L Y_i(x)Y_j(x) dx = 0$$

$$
\begin{align*}
\left\langle M\left[ Y_1 \right], Y_1 \right\rangle &amp;\approx 0.597735 \rho L \\
\left\langle M\left[ Y_2 \right], Y_2 \right\rangle &amp;\approx 0.519889 \rho L \\
\left\langle M\left[ Y_3 \right], Y_3 \right\rangle &amp;\approx 0.507733 \rho L
\end{align*}
$$

则

$${Y_i}\left( x \right) = {c_i} \sin (\omega_i x),\;\;i = 1,2,3 \dots$$

其中

$$
\begin{align*}
c_1 &amp;= \frac{1}{\sqrt{0.597735 \rho L}} \\
c_2 &amp;= \frac{1}{\sqrt{0.519889 \rho L}} \\
c_3 &amp;= \frac{1}{\sqrt{0.507733 \rho L}}
\end{align*}
$$

因此

$$y\left( {x,t} \right) = \sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{Y_i}\left( x \right){\eta _i}\left( t \right)}$$

代入

$$\rho \sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{Y_i}\left( x \right)\frac{{{\partial ^2}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)}}{{\partial {t^2}}}} - T\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {\frac{{{\partial ^2}{Y_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)} = 0$$

所以

$$
\rho\int_0^L {{Y_j}\left( x \right)\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{Y_i}\left( x \right)\frac{{{\partial ^2}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)}}{{\partial {t^2}}}} {\rm{d}}x - T} \int_0^L {{Y_j}\left( x \right)\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {\frac{{{\partial ^2}{Y_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^4}}}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)} {\rm{d}}x} = 0
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
\ddot{\eta}_i + \omega_i^2 \eta_i = 0, \quad i = 1,2,3
\end{align*}
$$

通解为

$$
\eta_i = C_{i1} \cos \omega_i t + C_{i2} \sin \omega_i t
$$

初始值

$$
\begin{align*}
\eta_i(0) &amp;= \int_0^L y(0, t) \rho Y_i(x) dx = c_0 \rho \int_0^L x^2 Y_i(x) d x\\
\dot \eta_i(0) &amp;= 0
\end{align*}
$$

即解为

$$\eta_i = \eta_i(0) \cos \omega_i t$$

代入


$$
\begin{align*}
\eta_1(t) &amp;=0.398852c_0 \sqrt{\rho L} \cos \omega_1 t\\
\eta_2(t) &amp;=-0.187622c_0 \sqrt{\rho L}\cos \omega_2 t\\
\eta_3(t) &amp;=0.05941c_0 \sqrt{\rho L} \cos \omega_3 t
\end{align*}
$$

代回$y\left( {x,t} \right) = \sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{Y_i}\left( x \right){\eta _i}\left( t \right)}$即可

## 3.3

$$
\begin{align*}
\int_{0}^{L} \omega_i^2 Y_i(x)Y_j(x) dx &= \int_{0}^{L} \frac{{{\partial ^2}Y_i\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}Y_j(x) dx \\
&=\left . \frac{{{\partial}Y_i\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} \frac{{{\partial}Y_j\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} \right|_{0}^{L} - \int_0^L \frac{{{\partial}Y_i\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} \frac{{{\partial}Y_j\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} dx \\
&= (\frac{k}{T})^2Y_i(x)Y_j(x) - \int_0^L \frac{{{\partial}Y_i\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} \frac{{{\partial}Y_j\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} dx
\end{align*}
$$

同理有

$$\int_{0}^{L} \omega_j^2 Y_i(x)Y_j(x) dx = (\frac{k}{T})^2Y_i(x)Y_j(x) - \int_0^L \frac{{{\partial}Y_i\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} \frac{{{\partial}Y_j\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}} dx$$

所以

$$(\omega_i^2 - \omega_j^2)\int_0^L Y_i(x)Y_j(x) dx = 0$$

当$\omega_i \neq \omega_j$时

$$\int_0^L Y_i(x)Y_j(x) dx = 0$$

## 3.4

$$
\begin{align*}
\left\langle M\left[ Y_1 \right], Y_1 \right\rangle &\approx 0.597735 \rho L \\
\left\langle M\left[ Y_2 \right], Y_2 \right\rangle &\approx 0.519889 \rho L \\
\left\langle M\left[ Y_3 \right], Y_3 \right\rangle &\approx 0.507733 \rho L
\end{align*}
$$

则

$${Y_i}\left( x \right) = {c_i} \sin (\omega_i x),\;\;i = 1,2,3 \dots$$

其中

$$
\begin{align*}
c_1 &= \frac{1}{\sqrt{0.597735 \rho L}} \\
c_2 &= \frac{1}{\sqrt{0.519889 \rho L}} \\
c_3 &= \frac{1}{\sqrt{0.507733 \rho L}}
\end{align*}
$$

因此

$$y\left( {x,t} \right) = \sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{Y_i}\left( x \right){\eta _i}\left( t \right)}$$

代入

$$\rho \sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{Y_i}\left( x \right)\frac{{{\partial ^2}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)}}{{\partial {t^2}}}} - T\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {\frac{{{\partial ^2}{Y_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)} = 0$$

所以

$$
\rho\int_0^L {{Y_j}\left( x \right)\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{Y_i}\left( x \right)\frac{{{\partial ^2}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)}}{{\partial {t^2}}}} {\rm{d}}x - T} \int_0^L {{Y_j}\left( x \right)\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {\frac{{{\partial ^2}{Y_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^4}}}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)} {\rm{d}}x} = 0
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
\ddot{\eta}_i + \omega_i^2 \eta_i = 0, \quad i = 1,2,3
\end{align*}
$$

通解为

$$
\eta_i = C_{i1} \cos \omega_i t + C_{i2} \sin \omega_i t
$$

初始值

$$
\begin{align*}
\eta_i(0) &= \int_0^L y(0, t) \rho Y_i(x) dx = c_0 \rho \int_0^L x^2 Y_i(x) d x\\
\dot \eta_i(0) &= 0
\end{align*}
$$

即解为

$$\eta_i = \eta_i(0) \cos \omega_i t$$

代入


$$
\begin{align*}
\eta_1(t) &=0.398852c_0 \sqrt{\rho L} \cos \omega_1 t\\
\eta_2(t) &=-0.187622c_0 \sqrt{\rho L}\cos \omega_2 t\\
\eta_3(t) &=0.05941c_0 \sqrt{\rho L} \cos \omega_3 t
\end{align*}
$$

代回$y\left( {x,t} \right) = \sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{Y_i}\left( x \right){\eta _i}\left( t \right)}$即可
